Lisa LoCicero https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisa_LoCicero 0 Lisa LoCicero (born April 18, 1970) is an American actress, known for her role as Sonia Toledo in ABC soap opera One Life to Live and Olivia Falconeri in another ABC soap opera General Hospital.
